data.description: SPACIOUS 4 beds / 2 bath, split floor plan home situated on a large water-front lot is now for sale! This home has a long and welcoming foyer, TWO large living areas, Air-conditioned garage, corner bricked fireplace, tall ceilings, a large open kitchen with tons of cabinets, stainless steel appliances, 2 car garage and a covered back patio with oversized entertaining area. The primary bathroom has his / her dual vanities, a separate tub and walk in shower. Ample storage throughout the home with large walk-in closets and linen storage. The fully fenced - LARGE yard also includes a storage shed! High and dry to boot! This home really has it all!! Penn Mill Lakes has a community pool and playground. Assumable mortgage with a LOW rate of 4.875%! Inquire today!
